platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Enter the world of Rocky Balboa with this tactically rich boxing simulation. Whether you play as Adonis Creed Johnson or design your own pugilist, dazzling graphics and fluid controls immerse you in the action. Swipe and tap to throw uppercuts and dodge body blows, maneuvering a global roster of opponents into position for the knockout. Training minigames upgrade your skills between bouts, but youll need sharp eyes and quick reflexes to become the best.
